pro2E.model

Class Model

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • pro2E.model.Model

  • public class Model
extends java.util.Observable
     The Model class contains a list of AntenaArray objects. Each element in the list corresponds to a simulation and therefore a different antenna array.
    Author:
    pro2E - Team3
